      class  Health
      Health models a person's health.
      class  HospitalAdministrator
      Hospital Administrator controls the entire workflow of the ECS hospital.

      Limb Surgeon inherits from Surgeon with the ability to cure specific limb related illnesses.

      Organ Surgeon inherits from Surgeon with the ability to cure specific organ related illnesses.
      class  Patient
      The Patient class models behaviours which a ECS hospital's patient could have.
      class  Person
      The Person class specifies the behaviour of a person including Patient and Doctors.
      class  Surgeon
      Surgeon inherits from Doctors with specified skills including the ability to operate surgeries.
